msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, iminā vihārena viharato ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa me hoti ābādho. "
msgstr "While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset me, and that was an affliction for me. "

msgctxt "an9.41:14.15"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, ānanda, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya; "
msgstr "Suppose a happy person were to experience pain; that would be an affliction for them. "

msgctxt "an9.41:14.16"
msgid "evamevassa me ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa me hoti ābādho. "
msgstr "In the same way, when perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset me, that was an affliction for me. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.448, sc15
msgctxt "an9.41:15.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then I thought, "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.2"
msgid "‘yannūnāhaṃ nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ti. "
msgstr "‘Why don’t I, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enter and remain in the cessation of perception and feeling?’ "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato. "
msgstr "But my mind wasn’t eager for the cessation of perception and feeling; it wasn’t confident, settled, and decided about it. I didn’t see it as peaceful. "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then I thought, "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.5"
msgid "‘ko nu kho hetu, ko paccayo, yena me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’? "
msgstr "‘What is the cause, what is the reason why my mind isn’t eager for the cessation of perception and feeling, and not confident, settled, and decided about it? Why don’t I see it as peaceful?’ "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.6"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then I thought, "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.7"
msgid "‘nevasaññānāsaññāyatane kho me ādīnavo adiṭṭho, so ca me abahulīkato, saññāvedayitanirodhe ca ānisaṃso anadhigato, so ca me anāsevito. "
msgstr "‘I haven’t seen the drawbacks of the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, and so I haven’t cultivated that. I haven’t realized the benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling, and so I haven’t developed that. "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.8"
msgid "Tasmā me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’. "
msgstr "That’s why my mind isn’t eager for the cessation of perception and feeling, and not confident, settled, and decided about it. And it’s why I don’t see it as peaceful.’ "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.9"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then I thought, "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.10"
msgid "‘sace kho ahaṃ nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulaṃ kareyyaṃ, saññāvedayitanirodhe ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseveyyaṃ, ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati yaṃ me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandeyya pasīdeyya santiṭṭheyya vimucceyya etaṃ santanti passato’. "
msgstr "‘Suppose that, seeing the drawbacks of the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, I were to cultivate that. And suppose that, realizing the benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling, I were to develop that. It’s possible that my mind would be eager for cessation of perception and feeling; it would be confident, settled, and decided about it. And I would see it as peaceful.’ "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.11"
msgid "So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, aparena samayena nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulamakāsiṃ, saññāvedayitanirodhe ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseviṃ. "
msgstr "And so, after some time, I saw the drawbacks of the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception and cultivated that, and I realized the benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling and developed that. "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.12"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato. "
msgstr "Then my mind was eager for the cessation of perception and feeling; it was confident, settled, and decided about it. I saw it as peaceful. "

msgctxt "an9.41:15.13"
msgid "So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharāmi, paññāya ca me disvā āsavā parikkhayaṃ agamaṃsu. "
msgstr "And so, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, I was entering and remaining in the cessation of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, my defilements were ended. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "an9.41:16.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, ānanda, imā nava anupubbavihārasamāpattiyo na evaṃ anulomapaṭilomaṃ samāpajjimpi vuṭṭhahimpi, neva tāvāhaṃ, ānanda, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "As long as I hadn’t entered into and withdrawn from these nine progressive meditative attainments in both forward and reverse order, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.41:16.2"
msgid "Yato ca kho ahaṃ, ānanda, imā nava anupubbavihārasamāpattiyo evaṃ anulomapaṭilomaṃ samāpajjimpi vuṭṭhahimpi, athāhaṃ, ānanda, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "But when I had entered into and withdrawn from these nine progressive meditative attainments in both forward and reverse order, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.41:16.3"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

#. VAR: cetovimutti → vimutti (si, mr)
msgctxt "an9.41:16.4"
msgid "‘akuppā me cetovimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more future lives.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.41:16.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.41:16.6"
msgid "Mahāvaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

